fier.','bi bi-phone-vibrate','1659264925.jpg',1,'2022-07-31 04:55:25','2022-09-08 03:55:38'),(6,'E-Commerce','e-commerce','Our extraordinary e-commerce solution can drag customers back to your store E-Commerce is the easiest and the quickest way to boost up your business. And e-commerce is the ‘behind’ any successful modern business also. Our team work on website development, mobile apps solution on iOS and Android platform for making your online business better.','bi bi-chat-square-text','1659265033.jpg',1,'2022-07-31 04:57:13','2022-07-31 04:57:13');
